namespace = archipelago_dynamic

country_event = {
	id = archipelago_dynamic.10011
	hide_window = yes
	trigger = {
	    AND = {
	        OR = {
                resource_stockpile_compare = {
                    resource = urp_000
                    value = 11
                }
            }
		    NOT = { is_variable_set = receive_reactor_1 }
        }
	}
	immediate = {
		add_resource = {
			urp_000 = -99999999
		}
        if = {
            limit = {                
		        NOT = { is_variable_set = checkVarNotForUse } 
            }
		    give_technology = { tech = "tech_progressive_reactor_1" }
		    give_technology = { tech = "tech_fusion_power" }
            set_variable = { which = receive_reactor_1 value = 1 }
        }
	}
}

	immediate = {

            set_variable = { which = receive_missiles_3 value = 1 }

	}

	trigger = {
	    AND = {
	        OR = {
                resource_stockpile_compare = {
                    resource = urp_000
                    value = 523
                }
            }
		    NOT = { is_variable_set = receive_farming_3 }
        }
	}
	immediate = {
		add_resource = {
			urp_000 = -99999999
		}
        if = {
            limit = {                
		        has_technology = "tech_progressive_farming_2" 
            }
		    give_technology = { tech = "tech_progressive_farming_3" }
		    give_technology = { tech = "tech_nano_vitality_crops" }
		    give_technology = { tech = "tech_food_processing_2" }
            set_variable = { which = receive_farming_3 value = 1 }
        }
	}
}
